     Turbo Dismount is a kinetic tragedy about Mr. Dismount and the cars       
     who love him. It is the official sequel to the wildly popular and         
     immensely successful personal impact simulator - Stair Dismount.          
                                                                               
     The highlights of this experience are multiple vehicles, an awesome       
     replay system, level editing features, high-speed physics and an          
     indiscriminate sense of style.                                            
                                                                               
     The purpose of the game is simple - damage awards points. It is up        
     to you to try different combinations of obstacles, vehicles, poses        
     and levels to make it to the top of the leaderboards. To support          
     friendly rivalry, Turbo Dismount supports placing a photo of your         
     friend on the face of Mr. Dismount - such a delightful way to             
     express one's emotions!
